      <p class="- topic/p ">You must create the System Properties record under the Apttus-Adobe eSignature Properties
         custom setting with the API Name <apiname class="+ topic/keyword pr-d/apiname ">ApttusAdobeESignatureProperties__c.
         </apiname>
      </p>
      <note type="note" class="- topic/note ">
         <p class="- topic/p ">You need to configure the Apttus-Adobe eSignature Properties custom setting with Apttus_Echosign namespace when sending an agreement for eSignature. </p>
